[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "しかし、昔は我関せずという感じだったお前さんが\n九偉人の問題を解決したいと言い出すとはねえ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00722",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "昔の私は知らないけど……\n多分一緒に暮らしている家族の影響なんだと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00723",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "まあねえ。おっさんやフロッケと一緒に居ると、\nもっと成長しなきゃって思っちゃうよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00724",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "もちろん、一番はハイディ、あんたの影響よ。\n記憶を失っても、相棒としてそばで支えてくれた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00725",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "お、おう……そう正面から言われると……\n照れちゃうよ……はは",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00726",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ああ……いい仲間に巡り合えたんだね。\nこれからも大切にしてやりなよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00727",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "はーい……そうだ、昔の私ってどんなだったの？\n我関せずって、ヘルトみたいに自由気ままな感じ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00728",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "まぁ、自分の動きたいように動くって意味では\nヘル兄と少し似ているかもね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00729",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "似ていると言われると、少しショックだわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00730",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ははは、まぁヴァレリアは威張ったりはしないから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00731",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "戦って、食べて、寝て……そんな感じさ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00732",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そうなのね……うーむ我ながら、\nあんまり兄弟愛とかなかったのかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00733",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でも今は、キューンが心配なのよ？\nヘルトとゼロに逆らえないだろうし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00734",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "ああ、ヴァレリアはキューンとヤドヴィガについては\n妹だからか、昔から結構気にかけてたね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00735",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガはいつも肌出してるから、\n風邪ひくよって服着せようとしてた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00736",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "おっ、なんかお姉ちゃんじゃ～ん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00737",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "からかわないの！\nでも、確かにお姉ちゃんしてたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00738",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "キューンが嫌いな野菜を、\nこっそり代わりに食べてやってたこともあったね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00739",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "ああ、あれそうだったんだ。\nてっきり足らなくて奪ってたのかと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00740",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "失礼な！　ちゃんと許可取ってもらってたのよ、多分！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00741",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……ねえ、ヘルトとゼロが旅行をしている間、\n私たちの監視はヤドヴィガとキューンになるわよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00742",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そのときに、隙を見て二人を説得したいの。\nイェルカ、シトリン、協力してくれる？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00743",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "もちろん。アタシはずっとお前さんたちの味方だよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00744",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "僕はずっと味方か分かんないけどね。ただまあ、\nおっかないヘルトに付きっきりは可哀そうだし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00745",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "向こうの陣営から引き抜くことで\nヘルト側の戦力を下げるのはいい案だと思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00746",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "シトリンは、ほんとヘルトのこと苦手よね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00747",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "まぁ、二人っきりの時に色々あったからね……\nそれに何より",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00748",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "僕も楽しいものが好きだけど、ヘルトと一緒にいると\n楽しいより怖いが勝つんだよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00749",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "あんたってなんとなく、常識って不自由の中で\n自由になろうとしてるように見えるしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00750",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "一方でヘルトってのは聞く限り常識に縛られない、\n自分自身が法って感じの自由に思えるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00751",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "おおう、僕が常識人……そんな風に\n見られていたとは驚きだ。ちょっと悔しいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00752",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そこで悔しがれるのがいいんだと思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00753",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "……ヴァレリア。相棒としてあんたの願い、叶えるよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_036_00754",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……ええ、頼りにしてるわよ、相棒",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00755",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]